title: Goku Royale 2 - Kiwi and Vlad's Vitriolic Venture in Vicinity of Vicious Villains and Valiant Victors
description: Goku Royale! The Squeakual, this time with a very old murder man and his ravenous little ankle biting child. Big Deal, a large keyboard faced cat calls many different parody I.Ps from across the land to come together and fight to death, for what reason? Only time will tell, instead for now the two rather opposing hitmen must do their jobs the best they can. Kiwi especially... she sucks at doing her job well...
